products.title: Intel Core i5-11400F Desktop Processor 6 Cores up to 4.4 GHz LGA1200 (Intel 500 Series & Select 400 Series Chipset) 65W
features: Compatible with Intel 500 series & select Intel 400 series chipset based motherboards
products.description: 11th Gen Intel Core i5-11400F desktop processor without processor graphics. Featuring PCIe Gen 4.0 support. Optimized for gaming, creating, and productivity. Discrete graphics required. Thermal solution included in the box. Compatible with 500 series & select 400 series chipset based motherboards. Refer to motherboard vendor for compatibility details. 65W.
